ActCanadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission Act
PrecisAppointment of NIRMALA NAIDOO of Calgary, Alberta, to be a full-time member of the Canadian Radio-television and Telecommunications Commission, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years; and her designation for the Alberta/Northwest Territories region, effective July 20, 2020.
